subject: Dogs
Dog Sledding
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
lead_paragraph: A sixth dog in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog race has died. Race officials said a dog on Alan Peck’s team died during a flight to Nome from Shaktoolik.
